{"pageid":52503,"pagename":"Maximum ranged hit","title":"Maximum ranged hit","displaytitle":"Maximum ranged hit","revid":14281765,"properties":[{"name":"smw-semanticdata-status","value":""},{"name":"description","value":"Maximum ranged hit is a term used to describe the highest amount of damage rangers can inflict. Currently the maximum ranged hit is 110 in PvM. In PvP, the max hit is ~79 with dragonstone dragon bolts (e) and max ranged damage gear."}],"content":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"hatnote\">This article is about a ranger's maximum hit. For other uses, see <a href=\"/w/Maximum_hit\" title=\"Maximum hit\">Maximum hit</a>.</div>\n<p><b>Maximum ranged hit</b> is a term used to describe the highest amount of damage rangers can inflict. Currently the maximum ranged hit is 110 in PvM. In PvP, the max hit is ~79 with <a href=\"/w/Dragonstone_dragon_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Dragonstone dragon bolts (e)\">dragonstone dragon bolts (e)</a> and max ranged damage gear.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\" role=\"navigation\" aria-labelledby=\"mw-toc-heading\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en-GB\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2 id=\"mw-toc-heading\">Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Maximum_hit_conditions\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Maximum hit conditions</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Calculating_your_maximum_ranged_hit\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Calculating your maximum ranged hit</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Step_one:_Calculate_the_effective_strength_level\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Step one: Calculate the <i>effective strength</i> level</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Step_two:_Calculate_the_base_damage\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Step two: Calculate the <i>base damage</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Step_three:_Calculate_the_bonus_damage\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Step three: Calculate the <i>bonus damage</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Maximum_hit_conditions\">Maximum hit conditions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?section=1&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Maximum hit conditions\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Maximum hit conditions\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Weapon: <a href=\"/w/Zaryte_crossbow\" title=\"Zaryte crossbow\">Zaryte crossbow</a></li>\n<li>Ammunition: <a href=\"/w/Ruby_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Ruby bolts (e)\">Ruby bolts (e)</a></li>\n<li>Opponent: <a href=\"/w/Corporeal_Beast\" title=\"Corporeal Beast\">Corporeal Beast</a></li>\n<li>Armour: None</li>\n<li>Other: Corporeal beast must be at full health.</li></ul>\n<p>As the Corporeal beast has 2,000 hitpoints, in theory Ruby bolts (e) would be capable of hitting a 400, when it has taken no damage. However, this effect has been capped at a maximum of 100; if a <a href=\"/w/Zaryte_crossbow\" title=\"Zaryte crossbow\">Zaryte crossbow</a> is used, the damage cap is increased to 110 upon activation.\n</p><p>Note that the max hit with ruby bolts (e) is a special effect of the bolts unaffected by equipment bonuses and Ranged level.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Calculating_your_maximum_ranged_hit\">Calculating your maximum ranged hit</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?section=2&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Calculating your maximum ranged hit\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Calculating your maximum ranged hit\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>With the addition of <a href=\"/w/Ranged_strength\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ranged strength\">Ranged strength</a> values, calculating a maximum ranged hit is now fairly easy.\n</p><p><b>Note:</b> The floor function means rounding the number down to the nearest whole number (eg. 19.9 -&gt; 19).\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Step_one:_Calculate_the_effective_strength_level\">Step one: Calculate the <i>effective strength</i> level</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?section=3&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Step one: Calculate the effective strength level\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Step one: Calculate the effective strength level\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"  alttext=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Effective Strength}}={\\Big \\lfloor }{\\big (}{\\text{Ranged Level}}+{\\text{Potion Bonus}}{\\big )}\\times {\\text{Prayer Bonus}}\\times {\\text{Other Bonus}}{\\Big \\rfloor }+{\\text{Style Bonus}}}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Effective Strength</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.623em\" minsize=\"1.623em\">&#x230A;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">(</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Ranged Level</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Potion Bonus</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">)</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>&#x00D7;<!-- × --></mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Prayer Bonus</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>&#x00D7;<!-- × --></mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Other Bonus</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.623em\" minsize=\"1.623em\">&#x230B;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Style Bonus</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle {\\text{Effective Strength}}={\\Big \\lfloor }{\\big (}{\\text{Ranged Level}}+{\\text{Potion Bonus}}{\\big )}\\times {\\text{Prayer Bonus}}\\times {\\text{Other Bonus}}{\\Big \\rfloor }+{\\text{Style Bonus}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/61ef629def735abcc568adbdea1e61ee4bd36d6b\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.838ex; width:103.12ex; height:4.843ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Effective Strength}}={\\Big \\lfloor }{\\big (}{\\text{Ranged Level}}+{\\text{Potion Bonus}}{\\big )}\\times {\\text{Prayer Bonus}}\\times {\\text{Other Bonus}}{\\Big \\rfloor }+{\\text{Style Bonus}}}\"/></span>\n</p><p>See the following table for the various bonuses values:\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Condition\n</th>\n<th>Bonus/Multiplier\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Potion (note: addition not multiplier)\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Ranging_potion\" title=\"Ranging potion\">Ranging potion</a>\n</td>\n<td>4 + floor(10% of level)\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Prayer\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Sharp_Eye\" title=\"Sharp Eye\">Sharp Eye</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.05\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Hawk_Eye\" title=\"Hawk Eye\">Hawk Eye</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Eagle_Eye\" title=\"Eagle Eye\">Eagle Eye</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.15\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Rigour\" title=\"Rigour\">Rigour</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.23\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Other\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Void_Knight_equipment\" title=\"Void Knight equipment\">Void ranger armour</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Elite_Void_Knight_equipment\" title=\"Elite Void Knight equipment\">Elite void ranger armour</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.125\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Black_mask_(i)\" title=\"Black mask (i)\">Black mask (i)</a> / <a href=\"/w/Slayer_helmet_(i)\" title=\"Slayer helmet (i)\">Slayer helmet (i)</a> (on task)<sup id=\"cite_ref-salvehelm_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-salvehelm-1\">&#91;a 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</td>\n<td>1.15\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Salve_amulet_(ei)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Salve amulet (ei)\">Salve amulet (ei)</a> (against <a href=\"/w/Undead\" title=\"Undead\">undead</a>)<sup id=\"cite_ref-salvehelm_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-salvehelm-1\">&#91;a 1&#93;</a></sup>\n</td>\n<td>1.2\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Dragon_hunter_crossbow\" title=\"Dragon hunter crossbow\">Dragon hunter crossbow</a> (against <a href=\"/w/Draconic\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Draconic\">draconic</a> monsters)\n</td>\n<td>1.25\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Style (note: addition not multiplier)\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Accurate\n</td>\n<td>3\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Longrange\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Rapid\n</td>\n<td>0\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div class=\"references-small hideQuotes\"><div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-salvehelm-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-salvehelm_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-salvehelm_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The slayer helmet and salve amulet bonuses do not stack when equipped simultaneously.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Step_two:_Calculate_the_base_damage\">Step two: Calculate the <i>base damage</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?section=4&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Step two: Calculate the base damage\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Step two: Calculate the base damage\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"  alttext=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Base Damage}}=1.3+{\\frac {\\text{Effective Strength}}{10}}+{\\frac {\\text{Ranged Strength}}{80}}+{\\frac {{\\text{Effective Strength}}\\times {\\text{Ranged Strength}}}{640}}}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Base Damage</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mn>1.3</mn>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mtext>Effective Strength</mtext>\n            <mn>10</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mtext>Ranged Strength</mtext>\n            <mn>80</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>+</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mrow>\n              <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n                <mtext>Effective Strength</mtext>\n              </mrow>\n              <mo>&#x00D7;<!-- × --></mo>\n              <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n                <mtext>Ranged Strength</mtext>\n              </mrow>\n            </mrow>\n            <mn>640</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle {\\text{Base Damage}}=1.3+{\\frac {\\text{Effective Strength}}{10}}+{\\frac {\\text{Ranged Strength}}{80}}+{\\frac {{\\text{Effective Strength}}\\times {\\text{Ranged Strength}}}{640}}}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/55bd04dfe9b2541112bcb15f14e77a2bcb94edaa\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -2.005ex; width:104.076ex; height:5.509ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Base Damage}}=1.3+{\\frac {\\text{Effective Strength}}{10}}+{\\frac {\\text{Ranged Strength}}{80}}+{\\frac {{\\text{Effective Strength}}\\times {\\text{Ranged Strength}}}{640}}}\"/></span>\n</p><p>If you are not using a special attack or effect:\n</p><p><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"  alttext=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}{\\big \\rfloor }}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Max Hit</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">&#x230A;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Base Damage</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">&#x230B;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}{\\big \\rfloor }}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/efa228e873ccc8e871f5e5c6e84a459107c6b7c7\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:27.258ex; height:3.176ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}{\\big \\rfloor }}\"/></span>\n</p><p>Otherwise, continue to step three.\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Step_three:_Calculate_the_bonus_damage\">Step three: Calculate the <i>bonus damage</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?section=5&amp;veaction=edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" title=\"Edit section: Step three: Calculate the bonus damage\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-divider\"> | </span><a href=\"/w/Maximum_ranged_hit?action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Step three: Calculate the bonus damage\">edit source</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"mwe-math-element\"><span class=\"mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y\" style=\"display: none;\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"  alttext=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}\\times {\\text{Special Bonus}}{\\big \\rfloor }}\">\n  <semantics>\n    <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n      <mstyle displaystyle=\"true\" scriptlevel=\"0\">\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Max Hit</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>=</mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">&#x230A;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Base Damage</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mo>&#x00D7;<!-- × --></mo>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mtext>Special Bonus</mtext>\n        </mrow>\n        <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n          <mrow class=\"MJX-TeXAtom-ORD\">\n            <mo maxsize=\"1.2em\" minsize=\"1.2em\">&#x230B;</mo>\n          </mrow>\n        </mrow>\n      </mstyle>\n    </mrow>\n    <annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}\\times {\\text{Special Bonus}}{\\big \\rfloor }}</annotation>\n  </semantics>\n</math></span><img src=\"https://wikimedia.org/api/rest_v1/media/math/render/svg/d2e0ffd145099e33bd5087fb3d694e310996fe5d\" class=\"mwe-math-fallback-image-inline\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"vertical-align: -1.005ex; width:44.094ex; height:3.176ex;\" alt=\"{\\displaystyle {\\text{Max Hit}}={\\big \\lfloor }{\\text{Base Damage}}\\times {\\text{Special Bonus}}{\\big \\rfloor }}\"/></span>\n</p><p>The following special attack/effect bonuses apply (note: the various bolts bonuses only apply when the special effect activates):\n</p>\n<table class=\"wikitable\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th>Attack/Effect\n</th>\n<th>Multiplier\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Special attacks\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Dark_bow\" title=\"Dark bow\">Dark bow</a> (<a href=\"/w/Dragon_arrows\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dragon arrows\">dragon arrows</a>)\n</td>\n<td>1.5\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Dark bow (other arrows)\n</td>\n<td>1.3\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Zaryte_crossbow\" title=\"Zaryte crossbow\">Zaryte crossbow</a> (<a href=\"/w/Enchanted_bolts\" title=\"Enchanted bolts\">enchanted bolts</a>)\n</td>\n<td>1.1\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\">Bolts' Special effects\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Diamond_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Diamond bolts (e)\">Diamond bolts (e)</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.15\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Dragonstone_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Dragonstone bolts (e)\">Dragonstone bolts (e)</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.45\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Onyx_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Onyx bolts (e)\">Onyx bolts (e)</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.15\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"/w/Opal_bolts_(e)\" title=\"Opal bolts (e)\">Opal bolts (e)</a>\n</td>\n<td>1.25\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks mw-collapsible\" data-expandtext=\"show\" data-navbox-name=\"Combat Mechanics\" data-collapsetext=\"hide\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" class=\"navbox-title\" id=\"navbox-title\"><div class=\"navbox-title-name-notplain\"><div class=\"navbar\" style=\"float:left;text-align:left;width:6em\"><div class=\"plainlinks noprint\" style=\"background-color:transparent;padding:0;font-weight:normal;font-size:xx-small;white-space:nowrap\"><a href=\"/w/Template:Combat_Mechanics\" title=\"Template:Combat Mechanics\"><span title=\"View this template\">v</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template_talk:Combat_Mechanics\"><span title=\"Discussion about this template\">d</span></a>&#160;<span style=\"font-size:80%\">&#8226;</span>&#160;<a class=\"text\" href=\"https://oldschool.runescape.wiki/w/Template:Combat_Mechanics?action=edit\"><span title=\"Edit this template\">e</span></a></div></div><span>Combat Mechanics</span></div></th></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\"><a href=\"/w/Combat\" title=\"Combat\">Combat</a></td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Attack_range\" title=\"Attack range\">Attack range</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Attack_speed\" title=\"Attack speed\">Attack speed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Auto_Retaliate\" title=\"Auto Retaliate\">Auto Retaliate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Autocast\" title=\"Autocast\">Autocast</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Combat_triangle\" title=\"Combat triangle\">Combat triangle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Special_attacks\" title=\"Special attacks\">Special attacks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hitsplat\" title=\"Hitsplat\">Hitsplat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Tanking\" title=\"Tanking\">Tanking</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Magical_melee\" title=\"Magical melee\">Magical melee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Magical_ranged\" title=\"Magical ranged\">Magical ranged</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Ranged_magic\" title=\"Ranged magic\">Ranged magic</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Maximum hit</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Maximum_magic_hit\" title=\"Maximum magic hit\">Maximum magic hit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Maximum_melee_hit\" title=\"Maximum melee hit\">Maximum melee hit</a></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Maximum ranged hit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Monster_maximum_hit\" title=\"Monster maximum hit\">Monster maximum hit</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Damage per second</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Damage_per_second/Melee\" title=\"Damage per second/Melee\">Damage per second/Melee</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Damage_per_second/Ranged\" title=\"Damage per second/Ranged\">Damage per second/Ranged</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Damage_per_second/Magic\" title=\"Damage per second/Magic\">Damage per second/Magic</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Mechanics</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Aggressiveness\" title=\"Aggressiveness\">Aggressiveness</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Flinching\" title=\"Flinching\">Flinching</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Hit_delay\" title=\"Hit delay\">Hit delay</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Retaliation\" title=\"Retaliation\">Retaliation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Retreat\" title=\"Retreat\">Retreat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Safespot\" title=\"Safespot\">Safespot</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Spawning\" title=\"Spawning\">Spawning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Successful_hit\" title=\"Successful hit\">Successful hit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Maximum_damage_cap\" title=\"Maximum damage cap\">Maximum damage cap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Tolerance\" title=\"Tolerance\">Tolerance</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Wander_radius\" title=\"Wander radius\">Wander radius</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/PJ_timer\" title=\"PJ timer\">PJ timer</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr class=\"navbox-group\"><td class=\"navbox-group-title\">Other</td><td class=\"navbox-list\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/w/Single-way_combat\" title=\"Single-way combat\">Single-way combat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Multicombat_area\" title=\"Multicombat area\">Multicombat area</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Singles-plus_combat\" title=\"Singles-plus combat\">Singles-plus combat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/w/Player_killing\" title=\"Player killing\">Player killing</a></li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mediawiki‐7bfb498f95‐gcmxr\nCached time: 20220511030829\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.109 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.332 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 160/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 6904/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 53/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 730/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.013/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 884975/367001600 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   43.449      1 -total\n 48.69%   21.156      1 Template:Reflist\n 33.27%   14.456      1 Template:Combat_Mechanics\n 18.17%    7.895      1 Template:Navbox\n 10.12%    4.397      1 Template:Ctg\n  5.38%    2.337      1 Template:Otheruses\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key en_osrswiki:pcache:idhash:52503-0!canonical!math=5 and timestamp 20220511030828 and revision id 14281765. Serialized with PHP.\n -->\n</div>","rawContent":"{{otheruses|a ranger's maximum hit|other uses|Maximum hit}}\n'''Maximum ranged hit''' is a term used to describe the highest amount of damage rangers can inflict. Currently the maximum ranged hit is 110 in PvM. In PvP, the max hit is ~79 with [[dragonstone dragon bolts (e)]] and max ranged damage gear.\n\n==Maximum hit conditions==\n*Weapon: [[Zaryte crossbow]]\n*Ammunition: [[Ruby bolts (e)]]\n*Opponent: [[Corporeal Beast]]\n*Armour: None\n*Other: Corporeal beast must be at full health.\nAs the Corporeal beast has 2,000 hitpoints, in theory Ruby bolts (e) would be capable of hitting a 400, when it has taken no damage. However, this effect has been capped at a maximum of 100; if a [[Zaryte crossbow]] is used, the damage cap is increased to 110 upon activation.\n\nNote that the max hit with ruby bolts (e) is a special effect of the bolts unaffected by equipment bonuses and Ranged level.\n\n==Calculating your maximum ranged hit==\nWith the addition of [[Ranged strength]] values, calculating a maximum ranged hit is now fairly easy.\n\n'''Note:''' The floor function means rounding the number down to the nearest whole number (eg. 19.9 -> 19).\n\n===Step one: Calculate the ''effective strength'' level===\n\n<math>\\text{Effective Strength} = \\Big \\lfloor \\big(\\text{Ranged Level} + \\text{Potion Bonus} \\big) \\times \\text{Prayer Bonus} \\times \\text{Other Bonus} \\Big\\rfloor + \\text{Style Bonus}</math>\n\nSee the following table for the various bonuses values:\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Condition\n!Bonus/Multiplier\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Potion (note: addition not multiplier)\n|-\n|[[Ranging potion]]\n|4 + floor(10% of level)\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Prayer\n|-\n|[[Sharp Eye]]\n|1.05\n|-\n|[[Hawk Eye]]\n|1.1\n|-\n|[[Eagle Eye]]\n|1.15\n|-\n|[[Rigour]]\n|1.23\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Other\n|-\n|[[Void Knight equipment|Void ranger armour]]\n|1.1\n|-\n|[[Elite Void Knight equipment|Elite void ranger armour]]\n|1.125\n|-\n|[[Black mask (i)]] / [[Slayer helmet (i)]] (on task)<ref name=\"salvehelm\" group=\"a\">The slayer helmet and salve amulet bonuses do not stack when equipped simultaneously.</ref>\n|1.15\n|-\n|[[Salve amulet (ei)]] (against [[undead]])<ref name=\"salvehelm\" group=\"a\"/>\n|1.2\n|-\n|[[Dragon hunter crossbow]] (against [[draconic]] monsters)\n|1.25\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Style (note: addition not multiplier)\n|-\n|Accurate\n|3\n|-\n|Longrange\n|0\n|-\n|Rapid\n|0\n|}\n{{Reflist|group=\"a\"}}\n\n===Step two: Calculate the ''base damage''===\n<math>\\text{Base Damage} = 1.3 + \\frac{\\text{Effective Strength}}{10}+\\frac{\\text{Ranged Strength}}{80}+\\frac{\\text{Effective Strength} \\times \\text{Ranged Strength}}{640}</math>\n\nIf you are not using a special attack or effect:\n\n<math>\\text{Max Hit} = \\big \\lfloor \\text{Base Damage} \\big \\rfloor</math>\n\nOtherwise, continue to step three.\n\n===Step three: Calculate the ''bonus damage''===\n<math>\\text{Max Hit} = \\big \\lfloor \\text{Base Damage} \\times \\text{Special Bonus} \\big \\rfloor</math>\n\nThe following special attack/effect bonuses apply (note: the various bolts bonuses only apply when the special effect activates):\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n!Attack/Effect\n!Multiplier\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Special attacks\n|-\n|[[Dark bow]] ([[dragon arrows]])\n|1.5\n|-\n|Dark bow (other arrows)\n|1.3\n|-\n|[[Zaryte crossbow]] ([[enchanted bolts]])\n|1.1\n|-\n!colspan=\"2\"|Bolts' Special effects\n|-\n|[[Diamond bolts (e)]]\n|1.15\n|-\n|[[Dragonstone bolts (e)]]\n|1.45\n|-\n|[[Onyx bolts (e)]]\n|1.15\n|-\n|[[Opal bolts (e)]]\n|1.25\n|}\n[[Category:Ranged]]\n[[Category:Mechanics]]\n\n{{Combat Mechanics}}"}